{"title":"E. Párkinson Procedimientos","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/General/UTD. E. Párkinson Procedimientos-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"E. Párkinson\\NProcedimientos\\NUTD 2025","guid":"c4rMfP6OVKa9P4BtQ8T8_w","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Procedimientos con dispositivos y técnicas\\Nlesionales en la enfermedad de Parkinson (EP)","guid":"nH9ETHBKJbNW9gmhLJKY2g","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"✔ Indicados en pacientes con fluctuaciones motoras, discinesias o temblor refractario","guid":"5Qoybw0jm00RBCxPiX4rjg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"✔ No modifican la progresión de la enfermedad → Solo mejoran síntomas","guid":"zsmdgU66iLZwHIpsjeC31A","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"1. Selección de\\Npacientes","guid":"MGMoCmxSqju1q5mYYC38og","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"✔ Criterios de\\Nelegibilidad:","guid":"IwuUMh2aBhnJXXlVa4vHFg","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"• Respuesta clara a levodopa","guid":"SUYOMXqlTVw4XSDlYJGLRA","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Fluctuaciones motoras y/o discinesias que reducen calidad de vida","guid":"--ghLvwJjPksXtYKzk2mHw","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Temblor refractario a levodopa (para estimulación cerebral profunda - DBS)","guid":"_RuaoBDFo2MfJ3YZL84wkw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"• Fluctuaciones no motoras en “off” (dolor, ataques de pánico, acatisia)","guid":"HmKYL1NOAg-pnK3e1giHUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"4","text":"✔ Reglas\\Ngenerales:","guid":"DulA5tcv8T9zB_sgXqGFuQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"⚠ No mejoran síntomas axiales refractarios a levodopa →\\NInestabilidad postural, disartria, disfagia, freezing en “on”","guid":"bFQV5H68bL0-e-jk3Wdjyg","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"⚠ Mejor respuesta preoperatoria a levodopa = mejor resultado postquirúrgico","guid":"BjGI4mHyxzaUEF1Ee-nXAA","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"⚠ Excepción → DBS mejora temblor refractario a levodopa","guid":"5VV_5ng1QBMOVyOCAhZ3qw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"2. Exclusiones y\\Nprecauciones","guid":"lNZwVuVW7jvtE2JOkuf0YQ","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"❌ Causas secundarias de parkinsonismo (fármacos, vascular, atrofia multisistémica)","guid":"ZOUe_VkPDhnkCLG0Q7mN0A","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"❌ Demencia o deterioro cognitivo significativo → No candidatos","guid":"vOL3d0s2Vf5aPT7DqOJS1w","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"❌ Psicosis activa, depresión no controlada, alto riesgo de suicidio\\N→ Requiere estabilización psiquiátrica antes de la intervención","guid":"6V2VLdRImCA3V4TcDGiCfA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"✔ Pacientes con deterioro cognitivo leve-moderado\\N→ Pueden considerarse para terapias de infusión","guid":"3rc3C8OzQDLdJKEQ15K52Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"1","text":"3. Evaluación\\Nmultidisciplinaria","guid":"iTgiMYMho6wSCK8aPyldCQ","children":[{"id":"20","parent":"19","text":"✔ Equipo especializado → Neurólogo, neurocirujano funcional, neuropsicólogo","guid":"42N-ngItTQ-7pgIBRUtydQ","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"19","text":"✔ Puede incluir → Psiquiatra, fonoaudiólogo, fisioterapeuta, terapeuta ocupacional, enfermería, trabajador social","guid":"zKoJfdCj_wCL0Mxswq-vjQ","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"19","text":"✔ Objetivos de\\Nla evaluación:","guid":"mdhaZ2xaXZGTI97BOBzSAg","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"✅ Confirmar diagnóstico de EP típica","guid":"4fFDRY-A-Pm1cGG_Pg8Fxw","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"✅ Asegurar prueba adecuada de fármacos dopaminérgicos","guid":"ef6fFsCikL2JjellrKPOAA","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"✅ Observar el cambio de “off” a “on” con levodopa","guid":"_ji5gu-0sV9D4h5xxQXN9w","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"✅ Evaluar riesgo quirúrgico","guid":"PmwV8drkCJ0dCOZtr1W66g","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"✅ Detectar deterioro cognitivo/demencia o problemas psiquiátricos","guid":"snuBhYF1DRf8OBvp83PJMQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"22","text":"✅ Educar sobre opciones terapéuticas, riesgos, beneficios y expectativas realistas","guid":"lZHf3ZPHCU0KslvupSdAQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"19","text":"✔ Decisión final:","guid":"hg3Q0hQGWBvYXfcUlsvCAg","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"📌 El equipo discute cada caso y selecciona la mejor opción terapéutica para el paciente","guid":"czxzeWKqFQZwpApOaAgTRA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"📌 Se informa al paciente y cuidadores la recomendación consensuada","guid":"8VKrz08i_nJmTn4N-YGllg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"0","text":"Selección del procedimiento en la\\Nenfermedad de Parkinson (EP)","guid":"czzhOzxDVBwDa4AKwwzIWA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"✔ Opciones disponibles para\\Ncomplicaciones motoras refractarias:","guid":"MWPjZ7arqdRaewtfo0Jaeg","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"• Estimulación cerebral profunda (DBS)","guid":"Crz076znpW92qFSw4NhC-g","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"• Infusión intestinal continua de levodopa-carbidopa (LCIG)","guid":"r5cZI101kj6uPFe82C9Mjw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"• Infusión subcutánea continua de apomorfina (CSAI)","guid":"1psOs4DpUuvmXKtGuWUJ5g","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"• Infusión subcutánea continua de foslevodopa-foscarbidopa (CSI)","guid":"D_O-RQJvMYKf--xTUcBGiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"32","text":"✔ Opciones\\Nlesionales:","guid":"jguhYtvq2OvWWirDJXWRpA","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"• Palidotomía unilateral con ultrasonido focalizado (FUS-MRI) → Para discinesias/fluctuaciones asimétricas","guid":"5TnqYfHVKwIEQeV5ZD7eXw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"• Talamotomía unilateral con FUS-MRI → Para temblor refractario","guid":"ntKiS9LW_xYwkPNdDrr-wQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"41","parent":"32","text":"✔ DBS es la única opción quirúrgica\\Npara temblor refractario a medicación","guid":"k3zTNdFCliw1Dn0vcClj0g","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"32","text":"1. Pacientes con complicaciones\\Nmotoras incapacitantes","guid":"uTuFL2d1mOAdvtMr81hlVA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"✔ DBS","guid":"wFLdhw-hJrhPPcwBxOi0aQ","children":[{"id":"44","parent":"43","text":"✅ Más datos de eficacia en ensayos clínicos","guid":"9uSRVm1wg3yFQYNbakcIXA","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"43","text":"✅ Se puede ajustar a lo largo del tiempo","guid":"BSWIHDkShYXFceUWnZcIag","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"43","text":"⚠ Requiere cirugía cerebral y generador de pulso","guid":"i0EjDiA1W0kJLtEIwAvBgw","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"43","text":"⚠ Riesgo de infección, hemorragia y fallas mecánicas","guid":"Vc6lL7gXHtBMf8ntviYTPA","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"✔ LCIG (Infusión intestinal\\Nde levodopa-carbidopa)","guid":"ShkMuf_2tbHhqGGQ0hN9MQ","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"✅ Reduce tiempo “off” y aumenta tiempo “on”","guid":"YUsZVeHC-TjXQSH7-PxOrA","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"⚠ Requiere colocación de tubo de gastro-yeyunostomía","guid":"2cPWiXnMv5NTexE7LcJ8ZQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"⚠ Necesita cuidados diarios del estoma y uso de bomba portátil","guid":"rTgYz3PJukiuvEGYEiq87Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"✔ CSAI (Infusión\\Nsubcutánea de apomorfina)","guid":"UlIODCago0MvgIF4L6EZOQ","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"✅ No requiere cirugía","guid":"LkvoI2sjxlU8yfmUa8Nekg","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"52","text":"⚠ Uso de aguja subcutánea → Reacciones en piel y nódulos","guid":"ScKBsbm8viFmQLe8Zrjo8Q","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"52","text":"⚠ Puede requerir levodopa oral adicional","guid":"DCVcnkagT2lukuuhJKen0A","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"52","text":"⚠ No disponible en EE.UU.","guid":"r8rBwb8ORYzOhwqUGD1EKA","children":[]}]},{"id":"57","parent":"42","text":"✔ CSI de\\Nfoslevodopa-foscarbidopa","guid":"mLQrcHTHTkrkuIGHx5RGzw","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"✅ Similar a CSAI (sin necesidad de cirugía)","guid":"HuRlihx1Z-luIUgFcdSiDA","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"✅ Aprobado en EE.UU., Canadá y Europa","guid":"EzUCtVenrbxaN8ub61k2kQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"⚠ Riesgo de infecciones y nódulos en el sitio de infusión","guid":"Ulf7wygntanhhjKa1BXbYA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"32","text":"2. Pacientes con\\Ntemblor refractario","guid":"UMDFERE_TZsDDdkbGvTm_w","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"✔ DBS → Más efectiva\\Nque otras opciones","guid":"gP9Oou97M_FErjAH0D6Rcg","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"• Núcleo ventral intermedio (VIM) → Solo mejora temblor","guid":"mmxYX588VHLnUgqGdPYYPQ","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"• Núcleo subtalámico (STN) / Globo pálido interno (GPi) → Mejora temblor, rigidez y bradicinesia","guid":"k7K61L2W4S6yVGajNCqaIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"✔ Talamotomía unilateral con FUS-MRI\\N→ Alternativa si DBS no está disponible","guid":"U-nXZQaINxvClHo24jnkYg","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"⚠ No trata fluctuaciones motoras de EP","guid":"eJRRSM4JMnSB1NlGmn5BlA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"32","text":"3. Pacientes en zonas con\\Nrecursos limitados","guid":"SYWbnvUGa1BWekOo-PAUKA","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"✔ Terapias con dispositivos requieren mantenimiento y seguimiento a largo plazo","guid":"K6gtgp4gEmI-hUPvkL-XdQ","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"✔ Alternativas:","guid":"8njRc0V0u4aoUFDY2voPuQ","children":[{"id":"70","parent":"69","text":"• Palidotomía unilateral (FUS-MRI) → Para complicaciones motoras","guid":"2A0bs9IiStJolMTFFQpFvQ","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"69","text":"• Talamotomía unilateral → Para temblor refractario","guid":"_DViUSXHwr8r-fv6Z0zebg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"0","text":"Estimulación cerebral profunda (DBS)\\Nen la enfermedad de Parkinson (EP)","guid":"x-U_MgEDEp67tYe5YRSIog","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"✔ Procedimiento quirúrgico más utilizado en EP avanzada","guid":"oxzzka0Lc291PhTBw_Yc8A","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"✔ Objetivo: Reducir fluctuaciones motoras y discinesias","guid":"AckGpiotpkKycG-caBj1_g","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"✔ Blancos\\Nprincipales:","guid":"eGHG2PqpB3k2oohGQnYOog","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"• Núcleo subtalámico (STN)","guid":"dB11jLAVwqoxGXGoHM6uCg","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"75","text":"• Globo pálido interno (GPi)","guid":"k6ZClVlG2WEzRRCn4OS-Dg","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"72","text":"✔ DBS en núcleo ventral intermedio (VIM) del tálamo → Solo mejora temblor","guid":"0xJTInF75idpw6kBJKq3eg","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"1. Procedimiento y\\Nmecanismo de acción","guid":"AYIM7hvA0Ps1H1g7B2ivXg","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"✔ Cirugía estereotáxica para implantar electrodos bilaterales","guid":"Mmgrkvww2A16wvYRiyZamA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"✔ Conectados a un generador de impulsos implantado en el tórax","guid":"t_LjrasB_HpgP1kDkQTtig","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"✔ DBS inhibe la hiperactividad del STN o GPi, restaurando la actividad tálamo-cortical","guid":"vd8VOxsU2OOa9ne2zPXgkA","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"79","text":"✔ No destruye tejido cerebral → Reemplazó a la palidotomía/talamotomía en centros especializados","guid":"AmJxb0WxSIT9t2DO-sFbWg","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"72","text":"2. Eficacia en EP con\\Ncomplicaciones motoras","guid":"TyygtTCaTF0V8r-dWxifmA","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"✔ Ensayos clínicos muestran\\Nmejoría significativa en:","guid":"tR4hWXSI4zkjWzq1Hfbreg","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Tiempo “on” sin discinesias","guid":"0x0nxv7mTHwSkMO0WNqkig","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Función motora","guid":"jM5UP_E5Yb2MlqIvegR0NQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Calidad de vida","guid":"pJVFlnro2o0PLChqYz8-Dg","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"✔ Estudios\\Nclave:","guid":"mHxwgNVzLA9YHF92l2wFmA","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"✅ INTREPID → DBS-STN mejoró tiempo “on” en 3 horas vs placebo","guid":"Me1FmjG4VXcQV92NGRFXzg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"✅ VA-NIH → DBS (STN o GPi) mejoró función motora en 71% vs 32% con terapia médica","guid":"kZRdpRLZz-P9OkgnsIbiNg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"✅ EARLYSTIM → DBS-STN en EP temprana mejoró calidad de vida y redujo complicaciones motoras","guid":"ReAQ_81Li_hG6q79EaDktQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"84","text":"✔ Comparación\\NSTN vs GPi:","guid":"hrPB2tGuvuneGNJFfH78ag","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• STN-DBS → Mayor reducción de medicación dopaminérgica","guid":"94cqx8Ak8Iepx1dMnzNyjw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• GPi-DBS → Mayor reducción de discinesias","guid":"22iBfyaCcDa2eiVJwcnQmA","children":[]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"84","text":"✔ Síntomas que NO\\Nmejoran con DBS:","guid":"Wuv_21YToABNSX51_ytiAQ","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"• Inestabilidad postural","guid":"7WJhSeg8QB-tpAszV4_HXg","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"96","text":"• Freezing en “on”","guid":"p1DuKHY-3RF_33dE-_yTWQ","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"96","text":"• Disartria","guid":"X1oBgXJcE5G_5MA1rtazjQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"96","text":"• Deterioro cognitivo","guid":"8zNkXMjdQO_Qcr6FcUAqSw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"72","text":"3. Duración\\Ndel beneficio","guid":"wYFTBOZiaxG67_f019qEZA","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"✔ Beneficio\\Nmantenido en:","guid":"xM3_3H6W0x9jZx8g7Fz5hw","children":[{"id":"103","parent":"102","text":"• Reducción de temblor y rigidez","guid":"tPy4vvO4lZf1KsZaolEFiA","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"102","text":"• Control de discinesias y fluctuaciones","guid":"-_ks6Ez-iPL8cdrUREVKfA","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"101","text":"✔ Bradicinesia y síntomas axiales → Deterioro progresivo a los 5 años","guid":"UYlv4yvK9kY0cwWO1zPhtw","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"101","text":"✔ Tasa de demencia a 10 años → 26% (similar a EP sin DBS)","guid":"NJgCS-kfngtrQ3JOrzTLLg","children":[]}]},{"id":"107","parent":"72","text":"4. Complicaciones y\\Nefectos adversos","guid":"0wzIe2UunQalztkCxymxgw","children":[{"id":"108","parent":"107","text":"✔ Quirúrgicas:","guid":"zSeF5lYa1PChoTrSCyOlLA","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"• Mortalidad: 0.6%","guid":"sOuanGGEFLm333y6UObZag","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"• Hemorragia intracerebral: 3.1-3. 9%","guid":"wbjsz-PeAyIbyP6z4X88Fw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"• Infección: 1.7-5.6%","guid":"cBBMwONgdO_Qvg5KZnlk3A","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"• Convulsiones: 1.1-1.5%","guid":"nSr8N_hK7Vdkby5mfOsPzQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"• Confusión/desorientación: 2.8-16%","guid":"ToI8EUt1pbb1aQsm-SgDEA","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"107","text":"✔ Relacionadas\\Ncon hardware:","guid":"l0_FtmootPZ0ZfFKhi7kRQ","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"• Malfunción o migración de electrodos → 5%","guid":"SSsetVTZW_Q_mXlyJlK74A","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"• Reacciones alérgicas → <1%","guid":"Zto-K-zH9auCkKScvY40Vg","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"• Vida útil del generador: 3-5 años (reemplazo quirúrgico)","guid":"WGv0CmQWtHx5Ro6gf3b7iw","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"107","text":"✔ Por estimulación:","guid":"8BjpmuXkuzEYKk0l0_bG1w","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"• Parestesias","guid":"dtHqVBFa8Bih6fMLjB3-vA","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"• Disartria","guid":"SZpLizKdX779-T2z71s8gg","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"• Apraxia de apertura palpebral","guid":"729LAXCwAIKuiyxuJSE6lg","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"118","text":"• Hemibalismo","guid":"dTe8NMbEEu-Eczquhbis7g","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"118","text":"• Ataxia","guid":"kTuKp4FhXakCi8OtD00ixg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"118","text":"• Discinesias","guid":"V4BRfFP1SXmNzoGjdMhPcw","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"118","text":"• Aumento de peso (8%)","guid":"pPV7cydfTUJmXn45l_Mepw","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"107","text":"✔ Neuropsiquiátricas:","guid":"p_M2sMtBtVHE2lwkmKIA-g","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"• Psicosis","guid":"Rg448KYBb-c-HFFCdDTesA","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"• Aumento de conductas impulsivas","guid":"Yr0jp5q2vhK6EAoPvM0UZQ","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"• Hipersexualidad","guid":"eJYzqimcRaaQ47mmtQm6nQ","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"• Aumento de apatía","guid":"KsBciVps5fIAST9L92fKuA","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"107","text":"✔ Riesgo de\\Nsuicidio:","guid":"GoRgt1URoo817Jo6x9jbEg","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"• 1% (similar a EP sin DBS)","guid":"wBxGLC_jeCW8fzLhotbCHg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"• Riesgo máximo en el primer año postoperatorio","guid":"MzeCbs9llzOvS9OihEJ7ZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"134","parent":"107","text":"✔ Síndrome de abstinencia por falla del generador → Síntomas parkinsonianos severos, fiebre, rabdomiólisis → Urgencia neurológica","guid":"vhlN0gAWDPKLURDqP5FBzA","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"72","text":"5. Consideraciones\\Nespeciales","guid":"Y_3Yupty5GGCUVLUJ2aVQg","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"✔ Contraindicaciones\\Nrelativas:","guid":"56ciwUCoZZSxLQSL_SHuSA","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• Marcapasos cardíaco (posible interferencia)","guid":"I9QmXgjoPcmVptgIXbz9UQ","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• Terapia con diatermia (riesgo de lesión cerebral)","guid":"qjQQuEK9a4Ho9EZtvwyM-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"135","text":"✔ Resonancia\\Nmagnética:","guid":"y4XRo8t6hF95xW41e5fJjQ","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"• Permitida con sistemas MRI-condicionales","guid":"LnQ3wo-c9-VbmyaU2qqksw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"• Límite: Máx. 1.5 Tesla y sin alteraciones del sistema","guid":"_xqMXavEt-DdQeEqydp_Bg","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"0","text":"Infusiones asistidas por dispositivos en la\\Nenfermedad de Parkinson (EP)","guid":"Sc8ePfKUG49_4634KPKi-Q","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"✔ Opciones\\Nprincipales:","guid":"UC3EuhZ25iwdW2SYAwQKQA","children":[{"id":"144","parent":"143","text":"1️⃣ Infusión intestinal de levodopa-carbidopa (LCIG)","guid":"o6lr7mxTXv82ckhlosALdw","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"143","text":"2️⃣ Infusión subcutánea continua de apomorfina (CSAI)","guid":"G-G0UHVX_d0J-xCExDAOBA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"143","text":"3️⃣ Infusión subcutánea de foslevodopa-foscarbidopa (CSI)","guid":"0CNwEss8awjYbFb5-JI-TA","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"142","text":"✔ Objetivo: Reducir fluctuaciones motoras al mantener niveles estables de dopamina","guid":"si_l2nJ3eEic8Ua6y-WWVQ","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"142","text":"1. Infusión intestinal continua\\Nde levodopa-carbidopa\\N(LCIG)","guid":"93Q_UBy18Dhg5B0TlcHiDg","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"✔ Alternativa a DBS en pacientes frágiles o sin interés en cirugía","guid":"LeMrJZiZpfvgtGOspGZ5Sg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"148","text":"✔ Mecanismo: Administración enteral continua de levodopa-carbidopa mediante bomba portátil","guid":"NUZVRaCfiaI9lStErT2XsQ","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"148","text":"✔ Indicaciones:","guid":"0VJWGjdP9g0Dx9nJd4neJQ","children":[{"id":"152","parent":"151","text":"• Fluctuaciones motoras graves"