 → ↑ homocisteína","guid":"7FS_R89ZL3JRn_gS_Q-X0g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"142","text":"2. Infusión subcutánea\\Ncontinua de apomorfina\\N(CSAI)","guid":"S5mELddHOw0t8PscJSsleQ","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"✔ Dopaminérgico potente y rápido","guid":"tJ193YmI_snVyEXNZ7tbbA","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"✔ Menos invasivo que DBS y LCIG → No requiere cirugía","guid":"-U1wiLr9G3MiQeAE8a_RIA","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"✔ No disponible en EE.UU.","guid":"pLuT7Tw7m3-tSNDs6nI9QA","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"Eficacia","guid":"uHRjY0wNlPaaNSSGwbeXNQ","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"✅ Ensayo TOLEDO → Reducción de 2.5 h en “off” vs placebo","guid":"-MG-7Lthp5Y0o1RAlITXNg","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"173","text":"✅ ↑ Tiempo “on” sin discinesias (2 h adicionales)","guid":"85jpe4R5Rp3kRfmYcV9PaA","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"169","text":"Administración","guid":"Zdo3nRjTj9OYm2ytZNJhRA","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"✔ Infusión continua por aguja subcutánea (abdomen, brazo o muslo)","guid":"p-zdK_pcjmKw63CUEK-n0w","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"✔ Premedicación: Domperidona (prevención de náuseas e hipotensión)","guid":"xB7j8OWft_mS3ug-66WiWw","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"✔ Monitoreo:","guid":"43nd8Lhiv8LaBkhPpgnkxQ","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"• ECG basal (riesgo de QT largo)","guid":"jCEowzU1C_vuqAEZRU9SuQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"• Coombs test y hemograma cada 6-12 meses (riesgo de anemia hemolítica)","guid":"-CuoePUPgJeBHMfZZ7H5SQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"176","text":"✔ Dosis usual: 4-7 mg/h por 16 h/día","guid":"CXebnbDKV_t8e5RTGipcvQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"183","parent":"169","text":"Efectos adversos","guid":"4fOU4sgOuDiRhLh2eLUAAw","children":[{"id":"184","parent":"183","text":"⚠ Locales:","guid":"JwT7Liv_b0lROnHNqr_c-w","childr